<L>__{interior mother's bedroom day}
<A>__{his mother takes out a stocking from her escritoire, and gives roderick twenty golden guineas.}
<C>__{mother}
<P>__{(gravely)}
<D>__{roderick, my darling, my wild boy, i have forebodings that our separation is to be a long one. i spent most of all night consulting the cards regarding your fate in the duel, and all signs betoke a separation. here is twenty guineas all that i have in the world and i want you to keep your father's sword and pistols, which you have known to use so like a man.}
